Partition function is weighted sum of contributions with different overlaps Y=\sum_{t} \delta_{x_t, x_t^*} 
\begin{align*}
Z(\epsilon_\text{t},t) = \sum_{Y=1}^T e^{\epsilon Y} Z_Y(t) \\
